5. Stolen vehicle/firearm workflow
Your schema already has vehicles.stolen and firearms.stolen columns, but I don't see any route or UI to set/clear them. Add a "Mark Stolen" button in leo.js vehicle/gun detail modals + PATCH /vehicles/:id/stolen and PATCH /firearms/:id/stolen (LEO-only), and surface it prominently in Dispatcher/DOT search too.


